CRUD REST api for storaging files(images) using GridFS/Multer

Upload a file (body must contain file:%image%)
POST localhost:8080/api/v1/files/upload

Get uploaded file
GET localhost:8080/api/v1/files/:filename

Delete uploaded file
DELETE localhost:8080/api/v1/files/:filename

Get all available files (Does not work properly yet)
GET localhost:8080/api/v1/files